.pl/im/8a/56/16/z23424394V,Anna-Smigulec-i-Pawel-Figurski.jpg', 'media_desc': 'Anna Śmigulec i Paweł Figurski', 'media_type': 'image', 'comments': []}, 'timestamp': 1563791093.047868}}